Before run go run main.go please:
1. create database names SAU-Test with username root and no password or edit credentials on database.go
2. run go get -u github.com/go-sql-driver/mysql
3. run go run main.go migrate to create the tables

To run docker please:
1. run docker build -t myapp:latest .
myapp will be your image name
2. make container with docker run -p 8080:8080 myapp:latest
you can use any port available like 8000:8080.
To access docker container use localhost:*local port*
local port is the first port based on the container

To run Unit Test:
1. run go test -v
